text: Tung Ya-ling (born 18 October 1971) is a Taiwanese taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in featherweight at the 1991 World Taekwondo Championships in Athens, by defeating Ayşegül Ergin in the final. She also participated at the 1989 and 1993 World Taekwondo Championships. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
